dc_title_s: 1:24,000 Quadrangle Polygon Boundaries: Russian River Watershed, California, 1996
dc_description_s: This layer represents the polygon coverage of USGS 1:24,000 scale quadrangles that are within the watershed boundaries of the Russian River basin.This shapefile contains the boundaries of the 24k quadrangles of California to be used for geographic reference.
